{"tid":1079391,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"[想死] 就來考車先來唔見銀包","createTime":"2019-03-27T02:26:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-29T00:18:41.000Z","uid":133001,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"a997d36a3a65d9f5747e1f93570135108b5c2feb","tid":1079391,"uid":133001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T02:26:56.000Z","msg":"『尋找失物』<br />\n2019-3-23 <br />\n2:25石籬商場紅的上車2:45到馬料水碼頭 一落車發現已太遲,架車就走左<br />\n失物係黑色Herschel銀包<br />\n有身份證、學牌、銀行卡，信用卡，學生證 ，$500。<br />\n個銀包好重要好有記念，希望快D搵返<br />\n已報失<br />\n錢冇左真係唔緊要<br />\n,最重要係揾得番個銀包因為真係好重要<br />\n,加上就來考車學牌都唔見埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一唔見野咩問題都出哂來<br />\n希望有心人執到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n感激<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知po去邊度好<br />\n銀包圖<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vRnrUbR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvRnrUbR.jpg&h=73438aa0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"58f5b4c774468781994570206981582ad7913390","tid":1079391,"uid":48286,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T02:30:36.000Z","msg":"冇咗個學牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64abdfc2975ce681123f6d3f1742f01321c4a094","tid":1079391,"uid":196924,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T02:31:49.000Z","msg":"冇學牌係可以參加駕駛考試<br />\n不過唔學得車咁解"},{"pid":"323f02ebb960db9db8d62f01aa1fdd9e03b82bfa","tid":1079391,"uid":133001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"58f5b4c774468781994570206981582ad7913390","tid":1079391,"uid":48286,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T02:30:36.000Z","msg":"冇咗個學牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fac